This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with video object segmentation, which is a core problem in computer vision. It may also belong to Multimedia (cs.MM) as it deals with video analysis. Additionally, it may belong to Machine Learning (cs.LG) as it discusses end-to-end sequential learning, Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) as it deals with developing algorithms for video object segmentation, and Graphics (cs.GR) as it involves visualizing and segmenting objects in videos.
